    "name": "GEM STAIR",
    "steam_appid": 3100100,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> GEM STAIR is a stage-based puzzle game.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >0. Gem</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100100/extras/5ecfa5ec40db3c367d6539e76c1c5734.avif?t=1730877313\" width=286 height=272 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The object with a number in the center that you see above is called a gem.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1. Select a stage</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100100/extras/b47945d13fb05f0bacb594136eb26f57.avif?t=1730877313\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100100/extras_big/b47945d13fb05f0bacb594136eb26f57.avif?t=1730877313 width=800 height=450 /></span>Select the desired stage from the screen above to start,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >you must clear the previous stage before you can select the next stage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2. Select a Tarot card</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100100/extras/7c2ab2a9225fd39a9b57d13324e6c7b8.avif?t=1730877313\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100100/extras_big/7c2ab2a9225fd39a9b57d13324e6c7b8.avif?t=1730877313 width=800 height=448 /></span>When you start a stage, you'll start with the tarot card selection screen shown above.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tarot cards are essential to completing the stage, and you can choose between one and three per stage to start.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100100/extras/24e749b28aff54ffd48a4fa1bf967d8e.avif?t=1730877313\" width=114 height=148 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tarot cards are also available via the above object in the lower right corner,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >to view and select the current stage situation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3. Player Turns</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100100/extras/8b992679a35d2a2dd47586ded02a7f9a.poster.avif?t=1730877313\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100100/extras/8b992679a35d2a2dd47586ded02a7f9a.webm?t=1730877313\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100100/extras/8b992679a35d2a2dd47586ded02a7f9a.mp4?t=1730877313\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once you have finished selecting your Tarot cards, you will start the game with a player turn.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Player turn does not end until you place a gem,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is when you can play your tarot cards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4. Playing Tarot Cards</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100100/extras/7a601e7efeea0807df25a28c17aac5a8.poster.avif?t=1730877313\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100100/extras/7a601e7efeea0807df25a28c17aac5a8.webm?t=1730877313\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100100/extras/7a601e7efeea0807df25a28c17aac5a8.mp4?t=1730877313\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can drag and drop Tarot cards to change the situation on the stage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5. Place a Gem</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100100/extras/cb0217efceaedff069915a0ad038ee86.poster.avif?t=1730877313\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100100/extras/cb0217efceaedff069915a0ad038ee86.webm?t=1730877313\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100100/extras/cb0217efceaedff069915a0ad038ee86.mp4?t=1730877313\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gems can be placed via drag and drop when conditions are met.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The conditions are as follows</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1. the gems must be of the same type</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2. the number written on the gem must be higher than the number placed on the far right.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6. CPU Turn </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100100/extras/06899ebb87ceeba66b3d4690a8e0fc18.poster.avif?t=1730877313\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100100/extras/06899ebb87ceeba66b3d4690a8e0fc18.webm?t=1730877313\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100100/extras/06899ebb87ceeba66b3d4690a8e0fc18.mp4?t=1730877313\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The CPU turn begins immediately after a player places a gem, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The CPU tries to place the leftmost gem they have.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If this is not possible, it will try to place the next gem.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7. Repeat</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When the CPU's turn ends, the player's turn begins again, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and the cycle continues to repeat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8. win and lose conditions</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100100/extras/3117d087619f66d258c1528e6a11d5bb.poster.avif?t=1730877313\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100100/extras/3117d087619f66d258c1528e6a11d5bb.webm?t=1730877313\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100100/extras/3117d087619f66d258c1528e6a11d5bb.mp4?t=1730877313\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The player wins when all gems in the player's hand are eliminated,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100100/extras/c538459b33b13412554f57b48f729887.poster.avif?t=1730877313\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100100/extras/c538459b33b13412554f57b48f729887.webm?t=1730877313\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100100/extras/c538459b33b13412554f57b48f729887.mp4?t=1730877313\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If any of the CPU's get rid of all their gems, they lose. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >9. In this game...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100100/extras/70878f432b2d6c2c820dc02a9fc1a2d0.avif?t=1730877313\" width=178 height=164 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are gems that have special effects.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are also</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100100/extras/a82b4e551a5b6fcc46f0da84c117c542.avif?t=1730877313\" width=340 height=164 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >special gems themselves.</p>",
